waiter, there's a waiter in my soup!

Of course, it's waiter — it waits.

Waiter, stop waiting, get out from his soup!

Alright, fine.

Waiter! There is headfruit in my soup! Dont you know Headfruit is made from the fruit of the Elowans? Are you just vile Thrynns?

I'm sorry, I didn't realize you'd said headcrab soup.

Waiter, there's tungsten in my soup!

You are wrong, sir. It's just wolfram.

Waiter! How much is half-life of this soup?

About 2.2 spoons, sir.

Waiter! What is the half-life of that other waiter!

As a matter of fact, he's currently going through a mid-life crisis at the moment. He has very radical hair.

Waiter! There's a handgun in my soup!

Sorry sir, the chef is Texan. 

Waiter! My soup is made of hydrazine!

Hail Hydrazine.

Waiter, there's  in my soup!

Well than  it! 

Waiter! There's a really old forum games post in my soup!

Oh don't worry about it, it's still alive.

 

Waiter, there are noodles that look like pool noodles in my soup! >:[

well what did you expect? our title is "nothin' but pool noodles" now eat your noodle a' la soup!

waiter! what's a tiny bender doing in my soup?

Oh god, we got a grey goo. Send the nukes.

Waiter! Did you just put a finger in my soup?

We serve you, sir! Your soup was too hot, we added some tap water to cool it.

Btw, Joe, fill the cooler cans, they are empty!

All filled.  with mercury fulmunate.

 

Waiter, there is a fly in my soup.

whats flying? WE NEED INFO!!!

waiter! there's a pronoun in my soup!

You ordered the alphabet soup.

Waiter! I have found an anomaly in my soup that is a portal to the past! I can find the Leghk inside!

Please, stop eating from the bath tube and put the stopper back.

Waiter! There's UFO - unknown fly object - in the soup.

sir, remember You have ordered the biggest dish on the menu; And that's what we have in the menu as a biggest dish

Waiter! There's and flux capacitor on my soup !

i dont think the soup bowl has enough capapcity

waiter a courupted tomato is in my soup

It's not a corrupted tomato, it's a fried tomato sauce. Because this soup is a borsch.

Chef! Looks like that tomato sauce was too old.
